<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakava<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>ṣaṁbulu 1298 gunēṁṭi śrīvīrabhānudēvasya pravardha
<lb n="2" break="no"/>mānā vijayarājyasaṁvatsaraṁbulu 31 srahi kuṁba sukla 10 yu paṁḍi
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tavāramunāṁḍu śrīnārasihyanāthuni bhōgaparīkṣa kaḷiṁggapārīkṣa pātradharmma
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dāsajīyana Adikāramaṁdu śiṣṭukavumahāsēnāpati pāṁcu<unclear>pra</unclear>karaṇa paṁca
<lb n="5" break="no"/>diveharaṇa vidyamanamuna saṁpradāyamu taṁtrasāniki śrīvīrābanudēva
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rājulaku [Āyu*]<unclear>ṣkāmā</unclear>rtthasidigā śrīnarasihyanaduniki saṁdanalagivēḷanu ca
<lb n="7" break="no"/>mara paḍimāṟanu prasādamu jītamu Appālu viḍiyala śālādigānu Oḍḍadi
<lb n="8"/>dēśāna lakumāvarana ceṟuvu kommu na<unclear>lu</unclear>vuṭlu kṣētramulōnu reṁḍuvuṭlu
<lb n="9"/>kṣētramu taṁtasāni bujiṁcci samara paṭṭaṁgaldu Ī dharmmu śrī<unclear>vai</unclear>ṣṇava rakṣa
<lb n="10"/>śrī śrī śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 0 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatruṇāpi kṛtō dharmmaḥ pālanīyō manīśibhiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatrurē<unclear>va hi sa</unclear>
<lb n="11" break="no"/>trusyāddharmma śatru na kasyacit <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

